      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since its original purchase. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely no swirl marks, rock chips, or door dings; it has been treated with a high-end ceramic coating to preserve the finish. Every panel gap is factory-perfect. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather upholstery shows no bolstering wear or creasing, and the original factory scent remains. All technological features, from the adaptive cruise control to the premium surround-sound audio system, function flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It comes with a complete binder of every service record performed exclusively by certified technicians, including a recent comprehensive multi-point inspection that returned a flawless report. The engine bay is detailed and pristine, and the undercarriage shows no signs of road salt or inclement weather exposure. This is a collector-grade vehicle for the discerning enthusiast who refuses to compromise on quality.",
